        "created_at": "2021-08-25T08:19:25.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I last had the 1998 La Conseillante in a late 2018 local vertical.   The oohs and aahs went to the 89/90, but while the 98 appeared tightly wound and young, it indicated future greatness.  I happen to think that big name 1998 Right Banks are still very youthful even at this stage.</p>",
