        "created_at": "2021-08-25T15:28:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The ch\u00e2teau are not a huge fan of the 1998, which was produced in a period of absentee ownership. It\u2019s a nice wine, but they felt it should have been better given the vintage\u2014and in the context of 1998 Cheval Blanc, Figeac, Evangile, it\u2019s hard not to agree.</p>",
